  "more_content": "<p><img id=\"1528321219995\" class=\" \" src=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174011/new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-macarons.png\" alt=\"new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-macarons\" data-image-large=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174011/large_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-macarons.png\" data-image-medium=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174011/medium_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-macarons.png\" data-image-small=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174011/small_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-macarons.png\" data-image-xsmall=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174011/xsmall_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-macarons.png\" data-image-thumb=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174011/thumb_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-macarons.png\" /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Got a sweet tooth? Come to New York and you&rsquo;ll feel you&rsquo;ve died and gone to heaven. We&rsquo;ve mentioned &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.newyorkerhotel.com/blog/the-best-ice-cream-shops-in-nyc/\">The Best Ice Cream Shops in NYC</a> and in the spirit of encouraging all of the New Yorker Hotel&rsquo;s guests to indulge in scrumptious delicacies, here are our top picks for the city&rsquo;s sweetest spots.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">Macarons</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://www.laduree.fr/en/\"><strong>Ladur&eacute;e</strong><br /></a><em>398 W Broadway, New York, NY 10012</em><br /><em>864 Madison Ave, New York, NY 10021</em><br />The most famous macaron makers in the world couldn&rsquo;t resist opening stores in NYC. &lsquo;Nuff said!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://www.nymacaron.com/\"><strong>La Maison du Macaron</strong><br /></a><em>132 W 23rd St, New York, NY 10011<br /></em>Proud to be the first macaron boutique in NYC, this P&acirc;tiserrie and Salon de Th&eacute; has created around 150 flavors.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><a href=\"https://macaronparlour.com/\">Macaron Parlour<br /></a></strong><em>44 Hester St, New York, NY 10002</em><br /><em>560 Columbus Ave, New York, NY 10024</em><br />Owned by a creative couple of bakers, Macaron Parlour has character, and so do their creations.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><img id=\"1528321314154\" class=\" \" src=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174139/new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-chocolate.png\" alt=\"new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-chocolate\" data-image-large=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174139/large_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-chocolate.png\" data-image-medium=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174139/medium_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-chocolate.png\" data-image-small=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174139/small_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-chocolate.png\" data-image-xsmall=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174139/xsmall_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-chocolate.png\" data-image-thumb=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174139/thumb_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-chocolate.png\" />Chocolate</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://mrchocolate.com/\"><strong>Jacques Torres</strong><br /></a><em>Various locations in NYC</em><br />Chocolate in New York means Jacques Torres. Check out their Chocolate Museum!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://www.lamaisonduchocolat.us/la-maison/en_us\"><strong>La Maison du Chocolat</strong><br /></a><em>Various locations in NYC</em><br />High-end French chocolate takes a whole new meaning in the iconic La Maison du Chocolat.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://www.li-lacchocolates.com/\"><strong>Li-Lac Chocolates</strong><br /></a><em>Various locations in NYC</em><br />&ldquo;Manhattan&rsquo;s oldest chocolate house&rdquo; makes artisan chocolate in all shapes and sizes.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><img id=\"1528321386459\" class=\" \" src=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174257/new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cupcakes.png\" alt=\"new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cupcakes\" data-image-large=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174257/large_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cupcakes.png\" data-image-medium=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174257/medium_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cupcakes.png\" data-image-small=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174257/small_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cupcakes.png\" data-image-xsmall=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174257/xsmall_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cupcakes.png\" data-image-thumb=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174257/thumb_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cupcakes.png\" />Cupcakes</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://www.tu-lusbakery.com/\"><strong>Tu-Lu&rsquo;s Gluten-Free Bakery</strong><br /></a><em>338 East 11th St, New York, NY 10003</em><br />A gluten-free and vegan-friendly bakery preparing healthy and delicious cupcakes (and cookies, brownies, muffins and much more).</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twolittleredhens.com/\"><strong>Two Little Red Hens</strong><br /></a><em>1652 Second Avenue, New York, NY 10028</em> <br />This bakery sells delicious cupcakes and classic American baked goods.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://www.magnoliabakery.com/\"><strong>Magnolia&rsquo;s Bakery</strong><br /></a><em>Various locations in NYC</em><br />Part of the Sex and the City locations tour, this bakery is famous for its decadent cupcakes.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><img id=\"1528321485399\" class=\" \" src=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174437/new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cookies.png\" alt=\"new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cookies\" data-image-large=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174437/large_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cookies.png\" data-image-medium=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174437/medium_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cookies.png\" data-image-small=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174437/small_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cookies.png\" data-image-xsmall=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174437/xsmall_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cookies.png\" data-image-thumb=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174437/thumb_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-cookies.png\" />Cookies</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://www.cookiedonyc.com/\"><strong>Cookie Do</strong><br /></a><em>550 Laguardia Place, New York, NY, 10012</em><br />That&rsquo;s right. Here is where you go to eat cookie dough with a spoon.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://schmackarys.com/\"><strong>Schmackarys</strong><br /></a><em>362 West 45th St, New York, NY 10036</em> <br />The most famous and unique cookie combinations await. Be ready to be surprised!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://www.glasersbakeshop.com/\"><strong>Glaser's Bakery</strong><br /></a><em>1670 1st Avenue, New York, NY 10128</em><br />Established in 1902, Glaser&rsquo;s Bakery is loved for its cookies, cakes, breads and pastries. Find out why they&rsquo;ve been around this long.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\"><img id=\"1528321581137\" class=\" \" src=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174611/new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-pie.png\" alt=\"new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-pie\" data-image-large=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174611/large_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-pie.png\" data-image-medium=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174611/medium_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-pie.png\" data-image-small=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174611/small_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-pie.png\" data-image-xsmall=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174611/xsmall_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-pie.png\" data-image-thumb=\"//cdn.traveltripper.io/site-assets/426_558_16502/media/2018-06-06-174611/thumb_new-yorker-sweetest-spots-in-nyc-pie.png\" />Pie</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://www.bubbys.com/\"><strong>Bubby&rsquo;s</strong><br /></a><em>120 Hudson St, New York, NY 10013</em><br /><em>73 Gansevoort St, New York, NY 10014</em><br />Quality ingredients combine into classic American comfort food that will beat anything you&rsquo;ve tried before.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://www.littlepiecompany.com/\"><strong>Little Pie Company</strong><br /></a><em>424 W 43rd St, New York, NY 10036</em><br />Pies made from scratch with all-natural, local ingredients and a special touch&hellip; Reminiscent of your grandmother&rsquo;s recipes.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><a href=\"http://peteespie.com/\">Petee&rsquo;s Pie Company<br /></a></strong><em>61 Delancey St, New York, NY 10002</em><br /><em>505 Myrtle Ave, Brooklyn, NY 11205</em><br />Organic, natural fair-trade pies made with classic and unique combinations. Gluten-free and vegan options available.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Go ahead and run to any of these shops for the best-tasting dessert ever! Don&rsquo;t forget to follow the <a href=\"https://www.newyorkerhotel.com/blog/\">New Yorker Hotel blog</a> to get the best advice for your trip to New York City!</p>",
